      "text": "Several national governments have created web sites to distribute a portion of the data they collect. It is a concept for a collaborative project in municipal Government to create and organize Culture for Open Data or Open government data. A list of over 200 local, regional and national open data catalogues is available on the open source Data Portals project, which aims to be a comprehensive list of data catalogues from around the world. Prominent examples include:"
