      "type": "paragraph",
      "id": "6f48fd17-3ad6-4f36-8f8b-acc17238d3d9",
      "text": "At the international level, the United Nations has an open data website that publishes statistical data from Member States and UN Agencies, and [[The World Bank]] published a range of statistical data relating to developing countries. The [[European Commission]] has created two portals for the [[European Union]]: the [[EU Open Data Portal]] which gives access to open data from the EU institutions, agencies and other bodies and the PublicData portal that provides datasets from local, regional and national public bodies across Europe."
